- `design-handoff/handoff.md` -- the canonical integration brief for the brain section; informs every strategy decision below: §1 variant selection (overridden by user to ship both rather than just A), §2-§4 what-to-ship and the static-HTML source shape that must be translated to App Router idioms, §5a top-bar nav addition with the `brain` link, §5b/§5c the cross-link target and the reverse-link placement, §6 BRAIN_PAL palette extension scoped to /brain, §7 the four `href="#"` placeholder substitution spots, §8 the three interactive surfaces and their state model, §9 the copy reference table for hero / section / footer strings, §10 the validation checklist that becomes the QA contract, §12 the explicit anticipation that the design source is reference rather than transcription
