- `.aide/intent.aide` -- the project root spec; informs the inherited static-export discipline (Next.js `output: 'export'`, no SSR / API / ISR / middleware), JetBrains-Mono-only typography, the fixed spacing scale, server-components-by-default, the brand voice rules, and the canonical external URL targets `https://github.com/aidemd-mcp/server` and `https://www.npmjs.com/package/@aidemd-mcp/server` that the brain section's external-link substitution inherits; also the source for the existing six-entry nav contract that this section widens to seven
- `.aide/docs/brain-aide.md` -- the canonical methodology doc that already renders inside the docs surface; informs the cross-link target for the Walkthrough's "the spec" footer card and the Cookbook's RELATED rail link, and the file the docs template must inject the reverse link onto without modifying the markdown itself
